### How to use it

You can use this crate in another Rust project by adding it to your `Cargo.toml`.

**Option 1: As a Local Path Dependency (for development)**
If you are developing another project locally alongside this one:
```toml
[dependencies]
rs-tree-sitter-languages = { path = "../path/to/tree-sitter-languages-rs" }
```

**Option 2: As a Git Dependency**
Once you push your changes to GitHub:
```toml
[dependencies]
rs-tree-sitter-languages = { git = "https://github.com/DakineMI/rs-tree-sitter-languages", branch = "main" }
```
